2.2.25. czekitout.check.if_positive_float_seq¶

if_positive_float_seq(obj, obj_name)[source]¶

Check whether input object is a sequence of positive floating-point numbers.

If the input object is not a sequence of positive floating-point numbers, then a TypeError is raised with the message:

The object ``<obj_name>`` must be a sequence of positive floating-point
numbers.

where <obj_name> is replaced by the contents of the string obj_name.

Parameters
objany type

Input object.

obj_namestr

Name of the input object.
